cuteSV is now available on the European Galaxy server. The European Galaxy server is part of the German Network of Bioinformatics Infrastructure (de.NBI), ELIXIR, and the European Science Cloud (EOSC-life). We hope that this badge will increase the cuteSV userbase in the community by pointing user to a combination of a graphical user-interface and compute resources.

Thanks for all the effort that has been put into cuteSV and for making it open source.
